==================== Input ====================
// The dominant css-in-js shape: bare top-level declarations with no enclosing rule.
// Only the embedded `format_to_ir` entry tolerates these (postcss accepts them);
// standalone `format()` rejects them as invalid, asserted in `parse_error_is_err`.

display: flex;
color: red;

&:hover {
  color: blue;
}

